OL,3,CTraineeship wages reinstated in
OL,4,Cgovernment u-turn
OL,6,FJersey's Minister for Social Security
OL,7,Fhas decided to reinstate the island's
OL,8,Ftrainee minimum wage.
OL,10,FFrom 1 September 2025, trainee minimum
OL,11,Fwages will be #10.50 for Year 1
OL,12,Ftrainees, and #11.75 for Year 2
OL,13,Ftrainees.
OL,15,FThe changes follow a survey by the
OL,16,Fisland's Chamber of Commerce, which
OL,17,Ffound industry leaders across the
OL,18,Fisland were struggling to recruit
OL,19,Fapprentices and trainees.
