OL,6,FThe trainee minimum wage was abolished
OL,7,Fat the start of the year when a
OL,8,Fstandard minimum wage was introduced,
OL,9,Fwhich increased to #13 from April.
OL,11,FBut a recent survey by Jersey's
OL,12,FChamber of Commerce found that 55 of
OL,13,F79 responding companies - around 70% -
OL,14,Fhad been negatively impacted by the
OL,15,Fchanges, with many saying they had
OL,16,Ffound themselves either unable or less
OL,17,Fwilling to employ apprentices.
