OL,3,CTraineeship wages reinstated in
OL,4,Cgovernment u-turn
OL,6,FThe survey revealed that the increased
OL,7,Fwage costs for trainees were placing
OL,8,Fpressure on smaller businesses, with
OL,9,Fmany employers fearing the ultimate
OL,10,Fimpact would be the complete loss of
OL,11,Fentry-level opportunities.
OL,13,F57 companies added that their
OL,14,Fbusinesses would benefit if the
OL,15,Ftrainee wage rate were reinstated.
