OL,3,CTraineeship wages reinstated in
OL,4,Cgovernment u-turn
OL,6,FThe rates will only apply to trainees
OL,7,Fworking on approved training
OL,8,Fprogrammes within the first two years
OL,9,Fof employment.
OL,11,FEmployers must also follow terms such
OL,12,Fas writing formal training agreements
OL,13,Fwhich clearly outline the programme's
OL,14,Fcontent, duration, and
OL,15,Fresponsibilities.
OL,17,FTrainees who start their job before 1
OL,18,FSeptember will receive the main wage
OL,19,Fof #13 per hour.
